21:14.374 --> 21:16.409
Why are you willing
to die for sex?

21:21.448 --> 21:24.684
Sex creates...

21:24.717 --> 21:26.953
Vulnerability,

21:26.986 --> 21:29.188
lets you be open,

21:29.221 --> 21:31.658
honest with
each other,

21:31.691 --> 21:34.193
share your
biggest fears.

21:34.226 --> 21:37.296
Sometimes,
you shouldn't share.

21:37.330 --> 21:39.732
Sometimes, you have to
just accept, right?

21:39.766 --> 21:41.701
Wrong.

21:41.734 --> 21:44.571
What you have to accept,
that's not for anyone
else to say.

21:46.072 --> 21:49.909
If you don't tell
your partner everything
that you're feeling,

21:49.942 --> 21:53.279
thinking, worrying about,

21:53.312 --> 21:56.182
then you aren't
fully connected.

21:57.617 --> 21:59.686
**

