22:39.859 --> 22:41.193
(CHUCKLES)

22:41.227 --> 22:43.362
And the bug spray
that we thought we packed?

22:44.464 --> 22:45.998
It was sunscreen.

22:46.032 --> 22:47.634
And then
when it started pouring,

22:47.667 --> 22:50.169
