22:51.370 --> 22:52.371
"Denny's."

22:53.239 --> 22:54.774
(CHUCKLES)

22:54.807 --> 22:56.809
And that's when I knew
I wanted to marry her.

22:56.843 --> 22:57.977
Great.

23:00.580 --> 23:03.783
