not Miami.

23:12.391 --> 23:14.994
And it was way better
than the bear trip.

23:16.429 --> 23:18.397
But I wasn't gonna tell
my fiancee's doctor about it.

23:19.432 --> 23:22.702
Sex...makes you real
with someone.

23:22.735 --> 23:24.036
