23:26.873 --> 23:29.175
I had the perfect man.

23:29.208 --> 23:33.412
He was...smart
and funny.

23:33.446 --> 23:36.182
He squeezed the sponge
after washing the dishes.

23:36.215 --> 23:37.249
(CHUCKLES LIGHTLY)

23:39.752 --> 23:43.690
Then one night,
I-I met some guy
and I had a few drinks,

23:43.723 --> 23:45.592
and, um...

23:45.625 --> 23:47.927
I got all tingly
and got really stupid.

23:48.928 --> 23:50.196
Never saw him again.

23:52.298 --> 23:53.432
Or my boyfriend.

23:55.468 --> 23:58.404
Sex can make us feel
incredibly close to someone...

24:00.206 --> 24:02.374
Honest,

24:02.408 --> 24:03.610
vulnerable.

24:06.345 --> 24:08.548
But sex is not
the goal.

24:10.817 --> 24:12.451
All the rest
of those things are.

24:13.986 --> 24:16.288
**

24:17.757 --> 24:18.991
She's the love
of my life.

24:20.159 --> 24:22.629
And I always thought
that we were strong

24:22.662 --> 24:24.997
and that we can overcome
anything together.

24:27.500 --> 24:29.001
But without sex...

24:31.237 --> 24:33.339
I don't know if...

24:33.372 --> 24:34.841
If we have enough.

24:36.008 --> 24:38.711
**

