Our language.

31:20.512 --> 31:24.183
Our way of sharing
who we are
with each other.

31:24.216 --> 31:25.484
And if we lose that...

31:28.254 --> 31:29.855
What if we don't
have enough?

31:30.689 --> 31:32.691
We'll still have...

31:34.260 --> 31:35.894
Honesty,

31:35.928 --> 31:37.063
intimacy,

31:37.997 --> 31:39.165
love,

31:39.898 --> 31:41.567
three kids.

31:41.600 --> 31:42.834
Two boys and a girl.

31:42.868 --> 31:44.303
(CHUCKLES)

31:44.336 --> 31:45.404
(CHUCKLES)

31:47.173 --> 31:48.407
(SNIFFLES)

31:52.011 --> 31:53.345
I love you
more than sex.

