31:56.782 --> 31:59.185
**

32:06.858 --> 32:08.194
(SNIFFLES)

32:10.396 --> 32:14.266
Does...this mean
you're getting the surgery?

32:16.868 --> 32:18.170
Yeah.

32:18.204 --> 32:20.472
**

32:23.375 --> 32:24.910
DR. PARK: 90 minutes
without a pulse in his leg.

32:24.943 --> 32:26.378
He's at high risk
for necrosis.

32:26.412 --> 32:28.280
DR. MELENDEZ:
Prosthetic successfully
sutured to aorta.

32:28.314 --> 32:30.349
CLAIRE: Almost done with
the distal right anastomosis.

32:30.382 --> 32:32.384
DR. MELENDEZ:
Careful not to narrow
the artery during suturing.

32:32.418 --> 32:33.619
CLAIRE: Mm-hmm.

32:33.652 --> 32:36.722
**

32:51.003 --> 32:52.471
(HEARTBEAT)

32:52.504 --> 32:54.940
DR. PARK:
Blood flow restored.
Good arterial pulse.

32:54.973 --> 32:57.076
DR. MELENDEZ: Good job
catching that clot,
Dr. Browne.

32:57.109 --> 32:59.011
If we'd waited any longer,
we'd have to amputate.

33:00.479 --> 33:01.547
Thank you.

33:01.580 --> 33:04.216
It...was a team effort.

33:04.250 --> 33:06.118
**

33:07.753 --> 33:10.256
DR. ANDREWS: Making incision
at the vaginal wall.

33:10.289 --> 33:12.091
Murphy, develop margins
at the lesion.

33:12.124 --> 33:13.325
SHAUN: Forceps.

33:13.359 --> 33:15.061
DR. ANDREWS: Nicely done.

33:15.094 --> 33:16.528
How you turned
your patient around.

33:17.463 --> 33:19.431
SHAUN: It was nice
when Tony told Jeanie

33:19.465 --> 33:20.999
he loved her
more than sex.

33:23.001 --> 33:24.002
He was lying.

33:25.637 --> 33:27.873
I told him that if he cared
about her at all, he had to.

33:29.541 --> 33:30.942
DR. ANDREWS:
Maybe it was the truth.

33:33.112 --> 33:35.114
It can be true
without him
knowing it's true.

33:37.049 --> 33:40.152
**

33:44.856 --> 33:46.958
(INHALES DEEPLY,
EXHALES SHARPLY)

33:46.992 --> 33:49.828
**

33:55.967 --> 33:56.968
What's wrong?

33:58.537 --> 34:02.040
Dr. Glassman told me
I have to accept things,

34:02.074 --> 34:04.210
but Jeanie said
to be open and honest.

34:04.876 --> 34:06.512
I agree with Jeanie...

34:06.545 --> 34:07.646
Whoever she is.

34:08.814 --> 34:10.616
It's your tattoo.

34:10.649 --> 34:12.084
(EXHALES SHARPLY)
Thank God.

34:12.118 --> 34:13.885
I thought
you hated my boobs
or something.

34:13.919 --> 34:15.254
It's incomplete.

34:16.888 --> 34:18.824
Didn't you have enough money
to pay for a full heart?

34:18.857 --> 34:20.559
(CHUCKLES)

34:20.592 --> 34:22.161
I got this in high school.

34:22.194 --> 34:23.395
It's incomplete.

34:23.429 --> 34:25.531
**

34:29.535 --> 34:31.069
(CLINKING)

34:36.742 --> 34:38.177
(SINGSON VOICE)
Not anymore.

34:40.346 --> 34:41.880
I got you.

34:41.913 --> 34:44.416
**

35:05.237 --> 35:06.638
Shaun?

35:08.574 --> 35:10.209
Dr. Glassman was right.

35:11.210 --> 35:12.644
It's not the tattoo.

35:13.145 --> 35:15.614
**

35:28.927 --> 35:31.497
We were able to restore
blood flow to his legs.

35:31.530 --> 35:32.598
He's gonna
be just fine.

35:32.631 --> 35:34.099
(EXHALES SHARPLY)

35:34.132 --> 35:35.534
Thank you so much,
Dr. Browne.

35:38.170 --> 35:40.472
Now that
he's out of the woods,

35:40.506 --> 35:43.775
you don't need to feel guilty
about questioning him.

35:43.809 --> 35:47.012
All the pain, paranoia,
and self-doubt...

35:48.013 --> 35:49.315
You deserve
to know the truth.

35:50.616 --> 35:51.817
He's just gonna deny it.

35:54.486 --> 35:56.087
Then you need to insist.

35:57.823 --> 35:59.258
(SIGHS)

35:59.291 --> 36:01.327
**

36:16.342 --> 36:18.210
Our relationship
was a stupid idea.

36:19.044 --> 36:20.946
Which made ending it
a smart idea.

36:21.580 --> 36:22.814
Simple, binary...

36:24.015 --> 36:25.116
And naive.

36:28.720 --> 36:31.223
I really underestimated
how hard this would be.

36:32.591 --> 36:34.560
**

36:36.127 --> 36:38.930
Yes, I've been having
second thoughts.

36:38.964 --> 36:40.499
I'm not saying we should
get back together...

36:40.532 --> 36:41.967
What are you saying?

36:44.903 --> 36:45.971
I don't know.

36:48.340 --> 36:49.341
Good.

36:51.743 --> 36:55.381
It's...good to know
that it's not easy.

36:58.183 --> 36:59.618
It's good to know
that it mattered.

36:59.651 --> 37:02.354
**

37:12.831 --> 37:14.700
Intimacy isn't
about a tattoo.

37:16.402 --> 37:19.571
And it's not about
touching or kissing

37:19.605 --> 37:21.840
or...even sex.

37:24.276 --> 37:28.380
It's about sharing
your biggest fears.

37:30.749 --> 37:31.750
Yes.

37:34.286 --> 37:35.587
What are you scared of?

37:39.124 --> 37:41.427
I love
being a pathologist.

37:44.363 --> 37:46.732
But every day
I walk into the lab,

37:46.765 --> 37:49.034
I am filled with doubt.

37:49.067 --> 37:51.370
Am I smart enough?
Am I capable enough?

37:51.403 --> 37:53.639
Do I really deserve
to be here?

37:54.940 --> 37:59.077
How long until
someone walks in
and exposes my fraud

37:59.110 --> 38:00.879
and has me removed
from the premises?

38:02.548 --> 38:04.650
Eventually,
those thoughts retreat.

38:06.284 --> 38:07.419
Until the next morning,

38:07.453 --> 38:09.488
when they all come crashing
back into my brain.

38:12.791 --> 38:14.292
That and pigeons.

38:15.727 --> 38:16.962
They freak me out.

38:17.896 --> 38:19.631
Hmm.

38:19.665 --> 38:21.967
**

38:24.302 --> 38:26.071
My biggest fear...

38:28.974 --> 38:30.609
...is that I'll be alone.

38:35.046 --> 38:37.849
If I don't get over this,
you'll leave.

38:38.484 --> 38:40.819
**

39:07.779 --> 39:09.114
We don't
have to have sex.

39:12.217 --> 39:14.986
Can we just hold each other
for a little bit?

39:15.854 --> 39:17.322
(EXHALES SHAKILY)

39:19.925 --> 39:21.460
I think I'd like that.

39:23.529 --> 39:26.064
**

39:50.589 --> 39:52.524
(EXHALES SHAKILY)

39:52.558 --> 39:55.360
**

40:01.667 --> 40:02.734
Shaun?

40:02.768 --> 40:05.871
**

40:11.342 --> 40:13.011
(INDISTINCT TALKING)

40:14.746 --> 40:15.814
Sash...

40:15.847 --> 40:16.848
Sash!

40:22.253 --> 40:23.589
(EXHALES SHARPLY)

40:37.803 --> 40:39.037
You should go.

40:40.906 --> 40:42.340
I don't know. Maybe.

40:42.373 --> 40:43.775
It can wait
till tomorrow morning.

40:45.310 --> 40:46.778
Eh, you were right.

40:48.413 --> 40:50.048
Everything you said
was right.

40:51.082 --> 40:52.484
But this is different.

40:55.453 --> 40:56.922
Shaun needs you.

40:57.889 --> 41:00.892
**

41:07.499 --> 41:09.635
(SOBBING)

41:09.668 --> 41:12.437
**

